{"tid":2178452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問及會否參與全民檢測 麥美娟：係自願性質，「時間容許」先做","createTime":"2020-08-28T11:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T14:41:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1b98e3537aa210bbf03e1eca0686b9e984c25bd9","tid":2178452,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"至於是否全體建制派議員均會參與當日在立法會進行的檢測？ 麥美娟就表示，由於檢測計劃屬自願性質，不會強迫議員接受檢測，相信建制派議員只要「時間容許」，便會進行檢測，強調「要睇大家工作安排」。她續指，自己較有興趣在各區的檢測中心進行檢測，不排除自己會在社區進行檢測，所以議員不一定要參與9月1日的立法會檢測。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/RG6SRF4QEJBB5BM7IRB4TXKR7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FRG6SRF4QEJBB5BM7IRB4TXKR7U%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=ff2d7bdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FRG6SRF4QEJBB5BM7IRB4TXKR7U%2F&h=2b3f8675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/RG6SRF4QEJBB5BM7IRB4TXKR7U/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c4bb7be2384340375a598c542620e5a82ea474","tid":2178452,"uid":359626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"47c091e46b6d005f8a2463a973843330626be7bc","tid":2178452,"uid":155818,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:35:58.000Z","msg":"拿, 我就睇娟娟頭既<br />\n佢檢我就檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f985cc02892abb36caab5d45b0382166236710","tid":2178452,"uid":12580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"講粗口既女仔"},{"pid":"83c8d6a6f4c766ea61b39baa6d69b9924a96c4df","tid":2178452,"uid":197726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"我記得呢個女仔怕痛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif